            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 0.4.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Focus Mode Status</strong> - Display active macOS Focus mode in the system status bar with the actual custom icon from your Focus configuration</li>
                    <li><strong>Optional Focus Name</strong> - Toggle to show Focus mode name alongside the icon</li>
                    <li><strong>Critical Battery Indicator</strong> - Battery icon turns red when below 10%</li>
                    <li><strong>Improved Battery Readability</strong> - Text shadow on battery percentage for better visibility</li>
